{"tid":775993,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"荷蘭反移民議員自殺亡　事前鋪片指控被穆斯林輪姦","createTime":"2018-08-11T15:43:14.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-12T12:22:43.000Z","uid":66260,"like":84,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":41,"replies":[{"pid":"adac6e6e1d7a79eda82f932025a19b320cbd287c","tid":775993,"uid":66260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T15:43:14.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180811/s00005/1533957480849\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180811%2Fs00005%2F1533957480849&d=hyevoFEhWk2UO4wypl8022i1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=ee5c119a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180811%2Fs00005%2F1533957480849&h=433c03ed\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180811/s00005/1533957480849</a><br />\n荷蘭傳媒報道，海牙市議會反移民的女議員迪勒（Willie Dille）在上載一段影片後自殺身亡，片中她聲稱一群穆斯林去年受人指使輪姦及恐嚇她。<br />\n<br />\n53歲的迪勒現為海牙市議會的議員，曾在2010年至2012年擔任自由黨（Party for Freedom）國會議員，該黨一直反對外來移民，並主張禁止伊斯蘭國家入境及成為公民。<br />\n<br />\n當地傳媒稱，迪勒是在本月8日自殺身亡。她日前將一段影片上載至互聯網。片段中，迪勒臉色蒼白、臉型瘦削。她指2017年3月15日的議會選舉日遭到一群穆斯林綁架、輪姦及虐待。歹徒威脅她在議會辯論期間保持沉默，她又收到一份死亡威脅。她聲稱事件是同屬自由黨的前國會議員Arnoud van Doorn指使，她指對方明顯不喜歡她。迪勒在片段結尾稱，自己正辭去議員席位，因為害怕暴徒會對其子女不利。<br />\n<br />\n據報道，有關短片已經被移除。<br />\n<br />\n荷蘭首相呂特（Mark Rutte）對迪勒的自殺表示哀悼，並表示他與海牙市長和司法安全部長已「密切接觸」。<br />\n<br />\n海牙市長Pauline Krikke發聲明稱，迪勒是一個對政治專注及熱情的人。自由黨地區負責人格蘭德斯（Karen Gerbrands）稱，迪勒毋須再承受她所經歷的事情及痛苦。而被迪勒指控為事件指示者的黨友Arnoud van Doorn則否認所有指控，並稱正尋求法律意見。<br />\n<br />\n警方發言人稱，迪勒從來沒有就事件正式報案。警方曾聯絡過她，希望她正式報案及提供詳細證據及資料，以開展調查工作，但她沒有作出任何行動。<br />\n<br />\n迪勒2016年在社交網站上稱，應該要向穆斯林放核彈，該番言論曾受廣泛批評。<br />\n<br />\n（霍士新聞/海外網）"},{"pid":"a4299d32b09b05c7d0df265fe0a1d4c55695bb13","tid":775993,"uid":35870,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T15:53:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bae2ff82087703c59f9a39a7a7c315123c722408","tid":775993,"uid":30830,"like":129,"dislike":1,"score":128,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T15:55:52.000Z","msg":"連荷蘭都咁<br />\n世界上除咗中国蝗仲有無嘢可以同穆斯林蝗一決高下"},{"pid":"3437f3e2a03f6b69663650010b392fcdd142287c","tid":775993,"uid":123774,"like":2,"dislike":22,"score":-20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T16:03:04.000Z","msg":"姦唔落 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23d13848ce0df83dc45a74e8d71eeceb229ec6b2","tid":775993,"uid":41508,"like":34,"dislike":1,"score":33,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T16:03:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"68f23c4489e52f803e07e90957962830b7d5a95e","tid":775993,"uid":121146,"like":41,"dislike":2,"score":39,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T16:07:36.000Z","msg":"伊斯蘭都有好人架  收多d啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ae5340ccd558c6fe72d31d9c6e8afc6aa6bb00c","tid":775993,"uid":38426,"like":47,"dislike":0,"score":47,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T16:07:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 啲回豬真係好恐怖<br />\n我信人類真係會滅亡了"},{"pid":"0c4f6058e9b1517328dcab7a01f1d832bf6c45cc","tid":775993,"uid":52946,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T16:19:01.000Z","msg":"支那夠唔夠班回撚鬥？"},{"pid":"9c7fb8384187d06c843f62a2e8658cbe05c9d3d0","tid":775993,"uid":80481,"like":42,"dislike":3,"score":39,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T16:19:12.000Z","msg":"好悲壯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif